"""
main.py  –  AE Auth Decline Summary Dashboard
==============================================
Reads  : AE_Auth_Decline_Summary.xlsx  (sheet "Auth Decline Summary")
Writes : AE_Auth_Decline_Summary_data.pdf
Excel columns (A-P):
  country | month | network | CP_CNP | BIN | cardtype |
  decisioning | tag | type | DECI_CD_ORIG | DECI_CD |
  TRANSACTION_ADVICE_XCD | ExRate | txns | AMT | amt_usd
PDF pages:
  1  Overall Transactions & Decline Rate
  2  Decline Rate by Decline Type
  3  Credit Related Decline (CRD)
  4  Card Type Distribution
  5  PLATINUM & INFINITE
  6  CASHBACK & MNH REWARDS PLUS
  7  SAADIQ & X CASHBACK
  8  STIP vs Non-STIP
  9  Card Present vs Card Not Present
  10 Other Declines Granular – Trend Lines
  11 Other Declines Granular – All Tables

CHANGES vs original:
  • Pages 5-7 (per-card): volume K/M and $K/$M rows now shown as LARGE TABLES
    (same visual size as a chart) instead of chart+table combos.
    Rate lines + waterfall bars + rate % tables are kept.
  • Large table helpers (plot_table_count_large / plot_table_usd_large) added
    to charts.py for bigger, more readable rendering.
"""
